title: TRIUNE - Slimepunks
description:
The coming of age story of a young man directly thrust into the relentless corruption of his parallel world.

Alos, a young man on the cusp of of graduating political prep school, is thrown from his censored life of comfort and luxury and directly into the chaos of the unknown world.

Join him as he narrowly escapes kidnapping, and finds himself being swept into a rebel political faction for protection. Put on board a crew of sky pirates, Alos must find a way out of his indentured servitude by using his honed digital computer talents to pay back the debt of his life.

Darkness is lurking behind the shadows, ever growing with the passing moons. 

This is planet Gemini.
